<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_ac1fc25c576a.aspx"><b>周颂·昊天有成命</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonac1fc25c576a">
<p>昊天有成命，二后受之。成王不敢康，夙夜基命宥密。於缉熙！单厥心，肆其靖之。</p>
