<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_7164c08b5c93.aspx"><b>载驱</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson7164c08b5c93">
<p>载驱薄薄，簟茀朱鞹。<br />鲁道有荡，齐子发夕。<br />四骊济济，垂辔沵沵。<br />鲁道有荡，齐子岂弟。<br />汶水汤汤，行人彭彭。<br />鲁道有荡，齐子翱翔。<br />汶水滔滔，行人儦儦。<br />鲁道有荡，齐子游遨。</p>
</div>
